 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m174e x61 h4 yeb1 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Love perfected. 1 John 2:5, 6; </div><div class="t m415 x4e h4 y14dd ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4:12, 16. </div><div class="t m2b6 x18 h4 y1507 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m308 x64 h4 y1343 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Comprehension of the all-embracing </div><div class="t m816 x28 h4 y1364 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">love of Christ. Eph. 3:17-19. </div><div class="t m21f x3 h20 y1519 ff3 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">III. The Crowning Virtue </div><div class="t m33d x18 h4 y13a3 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. Abiding virtues. 1 Cor. 13:13, first </div><div class="t m851 x4e h4 y1f3c ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">part. </div><div class="t m127 x8 h4 y10ef ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m162 x54 h4 y10ef ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Greatness of faith. Heb. 10:38, 39; </div><div class="t m224 x23 h4 y1c69 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">11:1, 6. </div><div class="t m2b6 x8 h4 y11c7 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m143 x54 h4 y1eb0 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Importance of hope. Rom. 8:24, 25. </div><div class="t ma2 x8 h4 y1ea1 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t ma11 x54 h4 y1d74 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Love the crowning virtue. 1 Cor. </div><div class="t m16f x23 h4 y1f19 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">13:13, last part. </div><div class="t m9ad x1c h20 yeab ff3 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Key Words: </div><div class="t m813 x56 h20 y1108 ff3 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t me60 x7b h20 y1108 ff3 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Fail. </div><div class="t m84a x91 h4 y1e26 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Two Greek words are used in </div><div class="t m3ed x58 h4 y1421 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1 Corinthians 13:8 for &quot;fail.&quot; The first, in </div><div class="t m552 x1c h4 y1ce6 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">reference to love&apos;s never failing, is from </div><div class="t m411 x1c h30 y1f3a ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ekpipto, </div><div class="t m3d0 xa8 h4 yb85 ff4 fs3 fc