n all else is gone. </div><div class="t mdbc x33 h4 y996 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[ 42 ] </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
